<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://bootswatch.com/4/superhero/bootstrap.min.css"
        crossorigin="anonymous">
        <title>plainDrop - Download File</title>

        <style>
            body {
                background-color: #eee;
            }
            .top {
                background: url('../public/background.jpeg');
                background-color: #111;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                background-size: cover;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                text-align: center;
                text-shadow: 1px 1px #000;
            }
            .bottom {
                background-color: #fff;
            }
            .block {
                text-align: center;
                color: #111;
                transition: 0.4s;
            }
            .block:hover {
                background-color: #eee;
            }
            .icon {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            input[type="file"] {
                display: none;
            }
            .custom-file-upload {
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 6px 12px;
                cursor: pointer;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
            }
            .second {
                margin-top: 35px;
            }
            .footer {
                margin-bottom: 0;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .custom-file-upload {
                transition: 0.4s;
            }
            .custom-file-upload:hover {
                opacity: 0.7;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">plainDrop</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarColor02" aria-controls="navbarColor02" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation" style="">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarColor02">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                <li class="nav-item active">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#features">Features</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#footer">About</a>
                </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="my-2 my-lg-0">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="regulations">Terms of use</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul> 
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="jumbotron top">
            <h1 class="display-2">plainDrop</h1>
            <p class="lead">The easiest way to drop your files.</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <% if (filename.length > 0) { %>
                <p class="lead">The file <b> <%= filename %> </b> is ready.</p>
                <p class="lead">Just press the "Download" button to get your file!</p>
                <form action="/files/download/<%=filename%>" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <input type="submit" value="Download" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                </form>
            <% } else { %>
                <h4>Sorry, the requested file is not available.</h4>
                <p class="lead">Please make sure that the link you have typed is correct or the file was not deleted.</p>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbotron bottom" id="features">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="block">
                        <div class="icon">
                            <img src="../public/document.png" alt="File Size">
                        </div>
                        <h4>Maximum file size?</h4>
                        <p class="lead">The maximum file size you can upload is 16 MB</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="block">
                        <div class="icon">
                            <img src="../public/link.png" alt="File Size">
                        </div>
                        <h4>Who can see my file?</h4>
                        <p class="lead">Only people who has got a link. The files are not shared to everyone.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="block">
                        <div class="icon">
                            <img src="../public/database.png" alt="File Size">
                        </div>
                        <h4>How long my file is available?</h4>
                        <p class="lead">You file is available as long as possible.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row second">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="block">
                            <div class="icon">
                                <img src="../public/money.png" alt="File Size">
                            </div>
                            <h4>How much it costs?</h4>
                            <p class="lead">You can upload your files completely free.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="block">
                            <div class="icon">
                                <img src="../public/law.png" alt="File Size">
                            </div>
                            <h4>How is responsible for the files?</h4>
                            <p class="lead">The site is not responsible for any illegal files. By uploading the files, you are accepting the following <a href="/regulations" target="_blank">regulations</a>. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="block">
                            <div class="icon">
                                <img src="../public/registration.png" alt="File Size">
                            </div>
                            <h4>Is registration necessary?</h4>
                            <p class="lead">No, you don't have to register to upload files.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbotron footer" id="footer">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <p class="lead">plainDrop</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <p class="lead">Owner&Site Creator</p> <b>Bartosz Stolarek</b>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <p class="lead"><a href="https://github.com/BartekStolarek/plainDrop" target="_blank">View Code on GitHub</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>